KUBOSHWE iphoyisa leJohahannesburg Metro Police Department (JMPD) kulandela ‘ukugwazelwa’ ngoR10 ngumshayeli wetekisi eSoweto. Okhulumela iJMPD, uChief Superintendent Wayne Minnaar uthe, iphoyisa belimisa itekisi ngasePretoria Glen eSoweto ngoMsombuluko ngoba ingenayo inumber plate nomshayeli wayo engaziphethe izincwadi zokushayela. “Ubanjwe oqotshweni igatsha eliphenya amaphoyisa kulo mnyango, umshayeli wetekisi ukuqinisekisile  ukuthi ugwaze ngoR10, uzoba ngufakazi wombuso,” kusho uMinnaar. Iphoyisa liboshiwe lagcinwa esiteshini samaphoyisa ePretoria Glen. UMinnar uthe inhloko yeJMPD, uMnuz David Tembe, iyaveva ngalesi sigameko. UTembe ubhale kutwitter waveza ukuthi basaqhubeka nokukhuculula inkohlakalo. Umsolwa kulindeleke ukuthi avele enkantolo kuleli sonto.